----

On 8 September every year, seven unlucky souls repeat six of the worst minutes of their lives. If they don't do it right, the entire human race faces a much worse time on a much grander scale. There's no end in sight, and they aren't getting any younger.

SCP Foundation Research and Containment Site-43 is the epicentre of a series of earth-shaking, reality-shattering cataclysms building to a crescendo which will only lead to the breaking of time itself... or the cycles of violence, ignorance and fear which fuel the fire. A confrontation between the forces of order and chaos is at hand, and the fate of all possible futures hangs in the balance.

However it ends, it's going to be memorable... If there's anyone left to remember it.

